categories: Category:Admirals and generals of the Sith Empire

nodes.text: A female admiral served the reconstituted Sith Empire during the Cold War with the Galactic Republic. During the war, her speeder was attacked by jungle beasts between the Dromund Kaas spaceport and Kaas City, on the Imperial capital planet of Dromund Kaas. Imperial Commander Rilan cited the incident with the admiral as one of the reasons behind investigation into what was stirring up the wildlife.
